## Component Responsibility Matrix

| Component | Responsibility | Runs | Can Modify Positions? | Authority |
|-----------|---------------|------|----------------------|-----------|
| **PositionReconciliation** | Broker sync, discrepancy detection | Every 5 min | ⚠️ Auto-correct only | OPERATIONAL |
| **RealTimePnLTracker** | P&L tracking, circuit breaker | Every tick | ❌ READ-ONLY | OPERATIONAL |
| **PositionAgingMonitor** | Holding limits, auto-close | Hourly | ⚠️ Auto-close only | OPERATIONAL |
| **SettlementManager** | T+1/T+2 tracking, failures | Continuous | ❌ NO | OPERATIONAL |
| **DisasterRecovery** | State persistence, recovery | Every 5 min | ✅ Recovery only | SYSTEM_CONTROL |
| **AlertManager** | Threshold monitoring, alerts | Continuous | ❌ NO | OPERATIONAL |

---

## MANDATORY Operations Requirements

1. **Position Reconciliation**: Sync with broker every 5 minutes
2. **Real-Time P&L**: Update on every market data tick
3. **Position Aging**: Monitor all positions against holding limits
4. **Settlement Tracking**: Track all trades through settlement
5. **State Persistence**: Snapshot system state every 5 minutes
6. **Health Monitoring**: Continuous system health checks
7. **Alerting**: Immediate alerts on threshold breaches

---

## PROHIBITED Patterns

❌ **Ignoring Discrepancies**: All discrepancies must be tracked and resolved
❌ **Skipping Reconciliation**: Position reconciliation cannot be disabled
❌ **Stale P&L**: P&L must update on every tick
❌ **Untracked Settlements**: All trades must have settlement records
❌ **No Backup**: System state must be persisted regularly
❌ **Silent Failures**: All failures must generate alerts

